  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support for the Strengthening of the Bicol Regional CSO Coordination DRR Hub</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.A well understood Manual of Operations of the HUB and Protocols
2.Appreciation and compliance of the CSO DRR HUB Checklist as monitoring tool for efficient hub operations
3.Scaled up HUB processes gained from the learning exchanges and  good stories and practices of CSOs on DRR and humanitarian work
4.Improved skills and capacities of CSO leaders in the HUB</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Within project duration, the following activities will be conducted to achieved the set objectives of the project: 
1.Setting up project Management and Orientations
2.Bi-monthly Hub Meetings and Writeshops
3.2 Peer Learning Exchanges
4.Training-Orientation based on Capacity Need of the Hub Members ( e.g. CHS and Safeguarding)
5.End of Project Assessment</narrative>
  </description>
